room_title: Escape room "Haunted Cemetery" by Hour Glass Escape Games in Bowling Green
room_address: 1043 Pedigo Way Suite 13, Bowling Green, KY 42103
room_description: You and your friends set out Halloween night to the old cemetery in town to investigate the legend of the missing caretaker.  Rumor has it that he was so obsessed with the dead that he attempted to bring the cemetery back to life through contact with the spirits.  Maybe you can put an end to all the rumors?  Or worse....maybe they will put an end to you.....
